            "title": "五索自爆最近因一事跟馬清鏗鬧分手 直指對方係大直男難相處 男方出招輕鬆挽回",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"五索自爆最近因一事跟馬清鏗鬧分手 直指對方係大直男難相處 男方出招輕鬆挽回\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/add02ef5aab77319843bac49e66934d5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250402/_2025040219503397105.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">五索自爆最近因一事跟馬清鏗鬧分手 直指對方係大直男難相處 男方出招輕鬆挽回</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>已婚大生銀行主席馬清鏗早前被《東周刊》獨家爆出與巨咪網紅「五索」鍾睿心（Rachel）暗交9年並誕下4名孩子，但五索其後沒有因此而被「滅聲」，反而越變越高調。早前，她與馬清鏗去瑞士旅行，更獲男方親自餵食，非常甜蜜；不過，五索日前就拍片透露上月因一事想跟馬清鏗分手。\n\n</p><h2>五索化身感情顧問</h2>\n<p>五索獲封「最強小三」，不少網民都向她請教「釣金龜」秘技，她日前拍片表示突然變了感情顧問，但就謂：「你哋係咁問我應唔應該分手？首先我唔係林作顧問，我冇收錢嘅，第二有咩事你哋會鬧我，所以我只可以同你哋分析，有咩情況下點樣做呢！」五索續分享心得，並以馬清鏗作例子，指對方難相處：「我覺得人係冇完美嘅，就當馬先生一個咁嘅人，佢好有錢對我好好啦，但其實佢都有好多缺點，佢真係一個好難相處嘅人嚟，佢係超級大直男啊！」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索日前拍片透露上月因一事想跟馬清鏗分手，更表示對方是一位大直男。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/931ec6b8e01737b52e26588791f44ed5/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_4_59_52_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索日前拍片透露上月因一事想跟馬清鏗分手，更表示對方是一位大直男。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"因為近日五索生蛇，被對方嫌棄好核突，令她好傷心。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef9612057d395415830eb36804de7a90/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_4_59_52_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        因為近日五索生蛇，被對方嫌棄好核突，令她好傷心。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索表示當下即爆喊，更坦言想跟對方分手。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee478122842fbed6117b53281541fd76/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_4_59_52_PM_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索表示當下即爆喊，更坦言想跟對方分手。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索說馬先生好有錢對她好好，但其實都有好多缺點。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/11712442af9b0b357972b2369b6aa7fa/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_4_59_52_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索說馬先生好有錢對她好好，但其實都有好多缺點。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索指當馬先生看見他生蛇的傷口，第一時間說好核突，走啊走啊！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b90b06b0263a84b29ffdac17aa3229da/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_4_59_53_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索指當馬先生看見他生蛇的傷口，第一時間說好核突，走啊走啊！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索覺得好傷心及無助。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e65e4c848b8018761983a268b9dfb994/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_4_59_53_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索覺得好傷心及無助。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當五索想分手之際，馬清鏗翌日買了機票，並跟五索說：「你咁大壓力，我哋一齊去歐洲玩。」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5b59635d4f4dbf7435d0c6e41b103110/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_4_59_54_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當五索想分手之際，馬清鏗翌日買了機票，並跟五索說：「你咁大壓力，我哋一齊去歐洲玩。」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索與馬清鏗去瑞士旅行，大曬靚相。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e5ec08888389f43ed0b85caac5777b3/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_32_39_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索與馬清鏗去瑞士旅行，大曬靚相。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"到高級餐廳用餐不忘拍片。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/935a6a8de72452df602dd324414ac63e/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_32_39_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        到高級餐廳用餐不忘拍片。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索更表示到瑞士住最貴的酒店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c431a6d082189cdb0bb386780090d181/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_32_40_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索更表示到瑞士住最貴的酒店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"五索表示雖然馬先生經常得罪她，但起碼有用行動安慰她。（《東周刊》圖片）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7dff46137e1448f12ee96cca93527cd3/2025-04/174359469416323.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        五索表示雖然馬先生經常得罪她，但起碼有用行動安慰她。（《東周刊》圖片）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>生蛇一事被對方嫌棄</h2>\n<p>五索續自爆最近發生一事，想跟對方分手：「我show 俾佢睇(生蛇 ) 冇晒頭髮，佢第一個反應係：『啊好核突啊，咩嚟㗎？唔好過嚟啊，係咪有菌啊，唔好俾我睇，走啊走啊』佢嫌棄兼鄙視，我個下即刻爆喊，搵我best friend 攬住喊，一齊諗方法，點樣戴假髮可以遮住嗰個位，而佢（馬清鏗）作為最親嘅人，連我嘅好朋友都不如，所以我個下真係好嬲啦！」\n\n</p><h2>讚馬清鏗用行動安慰</h2>\n<p>當五索想分手之際，馬清鏗相當識做，翌日買了機票，並跟五索說：「你咁大壓力，我哋一齊去歐洲玩」於是促成了早前的瑞士之旅。五索表示當下怒氣即消，並表示：「哇，每次想分手嘅時候，佢就做埋啲咁嘅嘢！所以一個人係唔會完美，就算佢把口唔叻，成日得罪我，但起碼有行動用心去安慰、關心我。我嘅擇偶條件就係，我好想另一半有啲行動，證明佢真係關心我或者愛我嘅。」最後，五索表示每個人想要的都不同，不可以要求一個人有晒所有嘢、包括靚仔、專一，有錢、識氹人等等，「如果你係咁就直頭唔好拍拖，如果你想繼續同呢個人行落去，你自己諗吓，只有一樣嘢，嗰個人俾唔俾到你想要嘅嘢你。」<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
