        {
            "title": "鄧麗欣誇遮樣男友按摩有水準為見張學友化靚妝  雲浩影想同Stephy表演風火輪舞技",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/cafee60de5fd01dcc4e71f42a09517c2/2025-04/page_34.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/903753ae0fb271f0b37787c7371d0102/3b2d2e77e641437d965633761bd4fa27-fad5106d04fac21d8ebdd8623b727f88-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ed1cb59fa4c\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ed1cb59fa4e\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鄧麗欣誇遮樣男朋友按摩有水準   雲浩影想同Stephy一齊表演風火輪舞技\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/cdb421d7472a78a956e0a0e045a8e200/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250402/_2025040219110168241.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鄧麗欣誇遮樣男朋友按摩有水準   雲浩影想同Stephy一齊表演風火輪舞技</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>鄧麗欣（Stephy）與雲浩影到銅鑼灣出席美妝活動，Stephy大談最心動時刻是見偶像張學友，為了合照而化靚妝，至於雲浩影則指海邊睇日落最心動，溫馨又浪漫。二人以女神Look現身，問到交流扮靚心得？Stephy搞笑稱是「兩代女神」，是自己太早封「女神」所致。\n\n</p><h2>Stephy男友即將曝光？</h2>\n<p>雲浩影笑言可以叨光Stephy，因為她是自己很欣賞的前輩，大讚她在演唱會表演「風火輪」出色，知道她是在頸受傷的情況下表演，做過針灸便上陣，敬業精神值得學習。Stephy談到頸傷，指演出時仍感到痛，不過上台便忘記了，她指是舊患令頸錐受壓力，需要較長時間的休息才能康復，問男友是否有愛的按摩？她笑言︰「有，很Work！」演唱會後可有和男友慶功？她指計劃中，早前上傳相片放閃，但男友被遮樣，她指是演唱會後台的合照，提到大家都期待正面相？她笑言將來或有機會，又指男友很大方，三場演出都在現場。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173251/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"美妝活動上，鄧麗欣（Stephy）被汽球搞到手忙腳亂！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/98510f22faab37c6e2964dd9b94a4b25/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_14_53_34_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美妝活動上，鄧麗欣（Stephy）被汽球搞到手忙腳亂！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173608/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stephy在演唱會後台與男朋友合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b222a273fdbdc8d85b7388ece12d1ae0/2025-04/20250330000545_0bd637517681e04f5dd5a93ed58122058bd31e5b.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stephy在演唱會後台與男朋友合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173252/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"美妝活動上，雲浩影說海邊睇日落最心動，溫馨又浪漫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/efcd5b2438ede37d1713dde18e8e1eaf/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_14_53_37.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美妝活動上，雲浩影說海邊睇日落最心動，溫馨又浪漫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173260/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stephy搞笑更正，與雲浩影是「兩代女神」，因為她太早封「女神」所致。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/595788385cb04e7ff5c82ec6ef224119/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_14_53_33_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stephy搞笑更正，與雲浩影是「兩代女神」，因為她太早封「女神」所致。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173741/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"雲浩影期待昇演唱會，同Stephy一齊表現風火輪！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b097dae0e526e438834f9c3ae4b119dd/2025-04/KK__7110.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲浩影期待昇演唱會，同Stephy一齊表現風火輪！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173262/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"3月時，鄧麗欣（Stephy） 辦3場紅館演唱會《STEP by STEPHY》，高潮位是從前組合Cookies成員楊愛瑾（Miki）、吳雨霏（Kary）、馬思恆（Helena）、陳素瑩（Gloria）、區文詩（Angela）及何綺玲（Elaine）現身演唱會，Cookies「七餅」相隔13年再合體唱《心急人上》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/428a3e0f23d2c250e60836d54566d0f1/2025-04/130A5039.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        3月時，鄧麗欣（Stephy） 辦3場紅館演唱會《STEP by STEPHY》，高潮位是從前組合Cookies成員楊愛瑾（Miki）、吳雨霏（Kary）、馬思恆（Helena）、陳素瑩（Gloria）、區文詩（Angela）及何綺玲（Elaine）現身演唱會，Cookies「七餅」相隔13年再合體唱《心急人上》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173264/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"ViuTV《CHILL CLUB 推介榜年度推介 24/25》，雲浩影角逐「年度女歌手」及「音樂第一歌曲獎（流行歌曲）」  。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/36214f300beccc37416e502f3c7ecc9c/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_14_58_24.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        ViuTV《CHILL CLUB 推介榜年度推介 24/25》，雲浩影角逐「年度女歌手」及「音樂第一歌曲獎（流行歌曲）」  。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173272/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stephy幾時post男朋友正面相？\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e0e7384df90747e5bdeff56d20044d19/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_14_53_35.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stephy幾時post男朋友正面相？\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173265/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Stephy面露有趣表情。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86075958a1278269f66a1f389ad657fd/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_14_53_31_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Stephy面露有趣表情。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173274/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"雲浩影早前畀人讚佢好似李嘉欣咁索。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/236285c9a454b381e9999affaefccc29/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_14_53_32.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲浩影早前畀人讚佢好似李嘉欣咁索。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4173275/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"雲浩影期待與Stephy一起表現風火輪。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da4eec794e4307e34549e3b9056ef811/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_14_53_36.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲浩影期待與Stephy一起表現風火輪。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>雲浩影羨慕Stephy事業愛情兩得意</h2>\n<p>問雲浩影可羨慕師姐Stephy事業愛情兩得意？她稱自己也很想開演唱會，問今年可成事？她希望今年可以，長遠目標是紅館，Stephy聞言即說屆時一齊表演「風火輪」，雲浩影笑指自己沒跳舞天份但會努力，Stephy亦希望可作巡迴演出。談到釗峰離開寰亞，雲浩影稱不是最後一日知道，今日會約對方晚餐，又指入行第一個音樂節目就是和他一同參與，有緣份，祝福對方找到新天地。問期望哪一位男歌手加盟，與之合作？雲浩影笑言陳奕迅和謝霆鋒，Stephy聞言也表示「好想」。 \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
